text: Maitham Jabbar Mutlag Al-Farttoosi (; born 10 November 2000) is an Iraqi footballer who plays as a defender for Al-Quwa Al-Jawiya in the Iraqi Premier League. ==International career== On 20 March 2019, Jabbar made his first international cap with Iraq against Syria in the 2019 International Friendship Championship. ==References== ==External links== * Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Iraqi footballers Category:Iraq international footballers Category:Association football defenders
